  "Name": {
    "English": "UTOPIA SPEEDER",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "乌托邦急速号",
    "TraditionalChinese": "烏托邦快速艇"
  },
  "NameLower": {
    "English": "Utopia Speeder",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "乌托邦急速号",
    "TraditionalChinese": "烏托邦快速艇"
  },
  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Exclusive Spacecraft",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属飞船",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊太空船"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A unique and exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">starship</span>, commemorating completion of the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Utopia</span> expedition, and contributions to the Utopia Foundation communal habitation project.<br><br>This versatile craft is plated with radiation-resistant armor, and engineered with an aerodynamic profile for agility during atmospheric flight.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘独一无二的专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>，纪念你完成<span class=\"name name-stellar\">乌托邦</span>远征，并且为乌托邦基金会的公共聚居地项目作出贡献。<br><br>这艘面面俱到的飞船配备有能够抵抗辐射的装甲板，并且能够借助符合空气动力学的工程设计在大气层内灵活飞行。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">领取</span>这艘飞船并将其添加至你的收藏，或者与你的当前飞船进行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，通过快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一艘獨一無二的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>，用以紀念<span class=\"name name-stellar\">烏托邦</span>探險的完成，以及對烏托邦基金會公共居住計畫的貢獻。<br><br>這艘多用途太空船鍍有抗輻射裝甲，並採用空氣動力學外形設計，可在大氣層飛行時保持敏捷。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">認領</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或是與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
